comments: Bane (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Goodwin (CLE) and absorbs the contact.
Goodwin (CLE) reaches in and makes contact with Morant's (MEM) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Allen (CLE) maintains his direct path and jumps vertically as he absorbs the body contact from Morant (MEM) on the driving shot attempt.
Adams (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Goodwin (CLE) and absorbs the contact.
Adams (MEM) makes marginal contact as he places a resting hand on Mobley's (CLE) body during his shot attempt in the post.
Goodwin (CLE) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Morant (MEM).
Morant (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position as he cleanly dislodges the ball during the pass to Garland (CLE).
Morant (MEM) releases from the contact as he and Garland (CLE) come together and separate in transition.
Morant (MEM) slides his pivot foot after receiving the inbound pass.
Goodwin (CLE) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Clarke (MEM) is the last to touch the ball before it goes OOB as he loses possession of the rebound on his own. CLE maintains possession of the ball.
Clarke (MEM) legally contests and cleanly blocks Love's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
